            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". While I have my reservations about it as a tool — it takes a very \"tick box\" approach to SEO that can be deceptive — it does enable soem key customisation that you need.",
